    Represents a <add-list-attribute> element in tiles.xml.
    TilesDefinition
    Represents a <definition> element in tiles.xml.
    TilesDefinitions
    An array of TilesDefinitions.

    Represents a <put-list-attribute> element in tiles.xml.
